movie.title: Guns N' Roses Appetite for Democracy 3D Live at Hard Rock Las Vegas
movie.title_english: Guns N' Roses Appetite for Democracy 3D Live at Hard Rock Las Vegas
movie.title_long: Guns N' Roses Appetite for Democracy 3D Live at Hard Rock Las Vegas (2014)
movie.description_intro: In November 2012, with a team of HD cameras rolling, the legendary, multi-platinum selling rock band Guns N' Roses took the desert by storm, performing a blistering set at The Joint in the Hard Rock Casino in Las Vegas. Clocking in at just under three hours, the band's explosive set includes all of their biggest hits and classic GNR staples including "Paradise City," "Welcome To The Jungle," "November Rain" and "Sweet Child O'Mine" plus songs from their critically acclaimed new album Chinese Democracy featuring the album-titled Top 10 hit single, "Better," "This Is Love" and "Catcher In The Rye."
